Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:21.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{Jet! Are you listening?!}Jet! Có nghe tôi không?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:32.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{S-Stop, please...}Làm ơn, dừng tay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.10,0:17:35.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{The grey ash is back.}Các anh đã lấy lại Tro Xám rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.31,0:17:37.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{Come on, let him go. I'm asking ya.}Thôi nào, thả anh ấy đi. Tôi xin các anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:40.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{Sorry to make you deliver\Nit all the way here.}Xin lỗi đã bắt anh mang nó đến tận đây.
