Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.17,0:17:46.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{Y-You!}Đồ khốn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.85,0:17:57.80,Main,,0,0,0,,{Get rid of him. Quickly!}Trừ khử hắn nhanh đi.
