Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:51.12,Main,,0,0,0,,{Roco!}Roco!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:19:00.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{Shit! Idiots!}Lũ ngu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:05.29,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Really, you've caused me enough trouble.}{\i0}{\i1}Trời, anh gây rắc rối cho tôi quá đó nha.{\i0}
