Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.59,0:19:15.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{Master... did you... see that right now?}Sư phụ, anh có thấy không?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:20.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. Don't speak anymore.\NI'll call a doctor right now.}Anh đã làm tốt, nhưng nói đủ rồi.\NTôi sẽ gọi bác sĩ đến.
